  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">UNHCR Secondment of Community Service Officer</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Afghan refugees in the Islamic Republic of Iran constitute one of the largest and long-standing refugee situation in the world.  In this framework, Switzerland and UNHCR were hosting the International Conference on the Solutions Strategy of Afghan Refugees in Geneva in May 2012 to find a multi-year solution strategy and define a roadmap to the protracted situation of Afghan refugees in the neighbouring countries, particularly Pakistan and Iran. This secondment is part of SDC&#x92;s contribution to support the host country Iran which is accommodating nearly one million Afghan refugees.</narrative>
  </description>
